name: Dave and Bambi Psych Engine Port (Homestead Update)
name_original: Dave and Bambi Psych Engine Port (Homestead Update)
description:
This is a psych engine port of Dave and Bambi with a few more songs.

This mod contains these songs:

  1. Literally every song from 2.5c of Dave and Bambi
  2. Applecore
  3. Bamangle
  4. Cheating 3
  5. Disclose
  6. Disruption
  7. Homestead
  8. Popcorn

Idk who created the original port so credits to the og Dave and Bambi  and Gapple developers, joolian, cotiles, and the creator of the psych engine port.

If the creator of the port wants me to take this down, I will.

The gameplay is not by me btw
